<style src="./VueView.css"></style>
<template src="./VueView.html"></template>
<script>
    let xhr = new XMLHttpRequest(),
	okStatus = document.location.protocol === "file:" ? 0 : 200;
	xhr.open("GET", ".about.txt", false);
    xhr.overrideMimeType("text/html;charset=utf-8"); // Default is UTF-8
	xhr.send(null);
	console.log(xhr.responseText);

    export default {
        name: "VueView",
        data() {
            return {
                areaName: "Vue",
                okStatus: okStatus,
                xxxr: xhr
            }
        },
    }
</script>
